## Faz 4: RAG Chat Pipeline (Gün 8-10)

### AI Clients
- [ ] GroqClient: HTTP request to Groq API
  - Model: llama-3.3-70b-versatile
  - Streaming support (SSE)
  - Error handling + timeout
- [ ] GeminiClient: HTTP request to Gemini API
  - Model: gemini-2.0-flash
  - Fallback client
- [ ] LlmService: Groq primary → Gemini fallback logic

### RAG Pipeline
- [ ] ContextBuilder: system prompt + chunks + history + question birleştir
  - Token counting (approximate: words * 1.3)
  - Sliding window for conversation history (son 5 mesaj)
  - Context truncation if exceeds limit
- [ ] RagPipeline.processQuery():
  1. Embed query
  2. Semantic search (top 5 chunks, min similarity 0.3)
  3. Build context
  4. Call LLM
  5. Return response + source chunks
- [ ] PromptBuilder: system prompt template
  - Hallucination prevention: "Answer ONLY based on context"
  - Source citation: "Reference the document when possible"
  - Persona support: professional/friendly/casual tone

### Chat Service
- [ ] ChatService.processMessage():
  1. Find or create conversation (session_id based)
  2. Save user message
  3. Run RAG pipeline
  4. Save assistant message (with source_chunks)
  5. Update conversation last_message_at
  6. Return streaming response

### Controller
- [ ] ChatController:
  - POST /api/chat/:chatbotId (JWT — owner test)
  - POST /api/chat/public/:chatbotId (no JWT — embed widget)
  - GET /api/chat/:chatbotId/conversations (JWT)
  - GET /api/chat/conversation/:convId (JWT)
- [ ] ChatMessageRequest DTO (message, sessionId)
- [ ] ChatMessageResponse DTO (message, sources, conversationId)
- [ ] SSE (Server-Sent Events) for streaming response

### Test
